Manchester City lost 2-1 to Crystal Palace in the Premier League on Monday . 
  Manuel Pellegrini won the title in May . 
  The last four Premier League winners have all left their jobs by the following year . 
  Jose Mourinho won the league with Chelsea in 2006 but was sacked in 2007 . 
  Carlo Ancelotti and Roberto Mancini were sacked after winning in 2010 . 
  Sir Alex Ferguson retired from Manchester United after winning the league in 2013 . 
 